sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor StoreManager
participant InventoryConsole
participant InventoryService
participant Utils
participant InventoryRepository
participant InventoryJson as inventory.json

== Remove Product ==
StoreManager->>InventoryConsole: Select "Remove Product"
InventoryConsole->>StoreManager: Prompt for product ID
StoreManager-->>InventoryConsole: productId
InventoryConsole->>InventoryService: removeProduct(productId)
InventoryService->>Utils: isPositiveId(productId)
InventoryService->>InventoryService: productExists(productId)
alt valid existing product ID
  InventoryService->>InventoryService: erase Product
  InventoryService-->>InventoryConsole: removal success
  InventoryConsole->>InventoryService: getAllProducts()
  InventoryService-->>InventoryConsole: products
  InventoryConsole->>InventoryRepository: saveProducts(products)
  InventoryRepository->>InventoryJson: write updated products array
  InventoryJson-->>InventoryRepository: persisted
  InventoryRepository-->>InventoryConsole: save complete
  InventoryConsole-->>StoreManager: Display success
else invalid product ID
  InventoryService-->>InventoryConsole: removal failure
  InventoryConsole-->>StoreManager: Display error message
end
